EN: The bark of the birch tree is very smooth.

ZH: 桦树的叶子是绿色的。
EN: The leaves of the birch tree are green.

ZH: 桦树的树干很直。
EN: The trunk of the birch tree is very straight.

ZH: 这片森林里到处都是桦树。
EN: Birch trees are everywhere in this forest.

