EN: The branches of the birch tree are very flexible.

ZH: 桦树的种子会随风飘散。
EN: The seeds of the birch tree scatter in the wind.

ZH: 这些桦树的树枝上开满了白色的花。
EN: The branches of these birch trees are covered with white flowers.

